# Step 5: Platform Settings Page

**Phase:** 12 -- Notifications, Monitoring & Polish
**Step:** 5 of 6
**Type:** Frontend implementation
**Depends on:** Step 3 (notification settings form), Step 6 (VPS stats panel), Phase 3 (GitHub App installation data)
**Blocks:** None

---

## Objective

Complete the `/settings` page with three organized sections: GitHub App connection status, notification preferences (Slack/Discord webhook configuration), and platform info (VPS monitoring stats). The page provides a central place for platform administration, replacing the current placeholder.

---

## Current State

The file `apps/dashboard/src/app/settings/page.tsx` has a placeholder:

```tsx
import { Placeholder } from "@/components/ui/placeholder";

export default function PlatformSettingsPage() {
  return <Placeholder title="Platform Settings" />;
}
```

---

